trans-unit.source: Allows the user to programmatically access the <see langword="system.web" /> group of the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: 允許使用者以程式的方式存取組態檔的 <see langword="system.web" /> 群組。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別無法被繼承。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.SystemWebSectionGroup> class refers to the `system.web` group within a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.SystemWebSectionGroup>類別是指`system.web`群組組態檔內。

trans-unit.source: You can use this type to access any of the sections contained in this group.
trans-unit.target: 您可以使用這個型別存取任何包含此群組中的章節。

trans-unit.source: The following code example shows how to obtain the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.SystemWebSectionGroup> object from the configuration file associated with an existing Web application.
trans-unit.target: 下列程式碼範例示範如何取得<xref:System.Web.Configuration.SystemWebSectionGroup>從現有的 Web 應用程式相關聯的組態檔的物件。
